---
layout: "base.njk"
title: "Kapcsolat – BagolykaLand Debrecen"
description: "Vedd fel velünk a kapcsolatot! Telefon: +36 30 364 9396. E-mail: fejlesztobagolyka@gmail.com. Debrecen belváros."
ogImage: "https://bagolykaland.hu/img/bagolykaland-csapat-bolglarka-portret.webp"
headStyles: |
  
      .contact-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        align-items: start;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .contact-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          gap: 2rem;
        }
      }
      .contact-info-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .contact-info-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 1rem;
        padding: 1rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e8f0ec;
      }
      .contact-info-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }
      .contact-info-item__icon {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        width: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .contact-info-item__label {
        font-size: .8rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: .05em;
        color: var(--clr-text-muted);
        margin-bottom: .25rem;
      }
      .contact-info-item__value {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #1D3557;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .contact-info-item__value a {
        color: #1D3557;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .contact-info-item__value a:hover {
        color: var(--clr-coral);
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .contact-form {
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      }
      .contact-form h3 {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #1D3557;
      }
      .form-group {
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      }
      .form-group label {
        display: block;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: .9rem;
        color: #4a5568;
        margin-bottom: .4rem;
      }
      .form-group input,
      .form-group textarea {
        width: 100%;
        padding: .75rem 1rem;
        border: 1.5px solid #d1ddd5;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: .95rem;
        font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
        color: #1D3557;
        background: #fafafa;
        transition: border-color .2s ease;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      .form-group input:focus,
      .form-group textarea:focus {
        outline: none;
        border-color: #5BB8AD;
        background: #fff;
      }
      .form-group textarea {
        resize: vertical;
        min-height: 140px;
      }
      .form-note {
        font-size: .8rem;
        color: #526374;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      }
      .form-note a {
        color: var(--clr-navy);
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 2px;
      }
      .map-placeholder {
        background: #e8f0ec;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2.5rem;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 3rem;
      }
      .map-placeholder p {
        color: #4a5568;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: .95rem;
      }
---


    <!-- PAGE HERO -->
    <section class="page-hero" style="background-color: #1D3557;" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="section-eyebrow fade-up">Kapcsolat</p>
        <h1 id="hero-heading" class="fade-up stagger-1">Lépj velünk kapcsolatba!</h1>
        <p class="fade-up stagger-2">Örömmel válaszolunk kérdéseidre és segítünk időpontot foglalni.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CONTACT CONTENT -->
    <section class="section section-cream fade-up" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="contact-grid">

          <!-- LEFT: Contact info -->
          <div>
            <h2 id="contact-heading" class="fade-up">Elérhetőségeink</h2>
            <p class="fade-up">Ne habozz felvenni velünk a kapcsolatot – megválaszoljuk kérdéseidet és segítünk megtalálni a gyermeked számára legjobb fejlesztési lehetőséget.</p>

            <ul class="contact-info-list fade-up">
              <li class="contact-info-item">
                <span class="contact-info-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">📞</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="contact-info-item__label">Telefon</div>
                  <div class="contact-info-item__value">
                    <a href="tel:+36303649396">+36&nbsp;30&nbsp;364&nbsp;9396</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="contact-info-item">
                <span class="contact-info-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">✉️</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="contact-info-item__label">E-mail</div>
                  <div class="contact-info-item__value">
                    <a href="mailto:fejlesztobagolyka@gmail.com">fejlesztobagolyka@gmail.com</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="contact-info-item">
                <span class="contact-info-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">📍</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="contact-info-item__label">Helyszín</div>
                  <div class="contact-info-item__value">Debrecen, Csokonai út 32.</div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="contact-info-item">
                <span class="contact-info-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">🕘</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="contact-info-item__label">Nyitvatartás</div>
                  <div class="contact-info-item__value">H–V 9:00–17:00</div>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
              {% set reviewVariant = "compact" %}
              <a href="{{ site.googleReview.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                 class="google-review-badge google-review-badge--light"
                 data-track="bk_google_review_click" data-track-variant="contact"
                 aria-label="Google értékelésünk: {{ site.googleReview.rating }} csillag, {{ site.googleReview.reviewCount }} vélemény">
                <svg class="google-review-badge__glogo" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92a5.06 5.06 0 01-2.2 3.32v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.1z" fill="#4285F4"/><path d="M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z" fill="#34A853"/><path d="M5.84 14.09a6.97 6.97 0 010-4.17V7.07H2.18a11.96 11.96 0 000 9.86l3.66-2.84z" fill="#FBBC05"/><path d="M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.07l3.66 2.84c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z" fill="#EA4335"/></svg>
                <span class="google-review-badge__stars" role="img" aria-label="{{ site.googleReview.rating }} csillag">★★★★★</span>
                <span class="google-review-badge__text"><strong>{{ site.googleReview.rating }}</strong>/5 · {{ site.googleReview.reviewCount }} Google vélemény</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- RIGHT: Contact form -->
          <div class="contact-form fade-up">
            <h3>Küldj üzenetet</h3>
            <form id="contact-form" action="/api/contact.php" method="post" novalidate>
              <div class="form-group">
              <label for="contact-name">Neved <span aria-hidden="true" style="color:var(--clr-coral);">*</span></label>
                <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="name" required autocomplete="name" placeholder="Pl. Nagy Éva" />
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
              <label for="contact-email">E-mail cím <span aria-hidden="true" style="color:var(--clr-coral);">*</span></label>
                <input type="email" id="contact-email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" placeholder="nev@email.hu" />
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
              <label for="contact-phone">Telefonszám <span class="form-optional">(opcionális)</span></label>
                <input type="tel" id="contact-phone" name="phone" autocomplete="tel" placeholder="+36 30 000 0000" />
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
              <label for="contact-message">Üzenet <span aria-hidden="true" style="color:var(--clr-coral);">*</span></label>
                <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" required placeholder="Írd le kérdésedet, gyermeked korát és miért keresel minket..."></textarea>
              </div>
              <!-- Honeypot — hidden from real users, catches bots -->
              <div style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;" aria-hidden="true">
                <input type="text" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />
              </div>
              <p class="form-note">
                Az üzenet elküldésével elfogadod az
                <a href="/adatkezelesi-tajekoztato/">adatkezelési tájékoztatót</a>.
              </p>
              <p id="contact-error" style="display:none;color:var(--clr-coral);font-size:.85rem;margin-bottom:1rem;text-align:center;"></p>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">Üzenet küldése</button>
            </form>
            <div id="contact-success" style="display:none;text-align:center;padding:2rem 1rem;">
              <div style="font-size:2.5rem;margin-bottom:.75rem;">✅</div>
              <h3 style="color:var(--clr-teal);margin-bottom:.5rem;">Üzenet elküldve!</h3>
              <p style="color:var(--clr-text-mid);">Köszönjük megkeresésedet! Hamarosan válaszolunk az e-mail címedre.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        {# ── TÉRKÉP ── #}
        <div class="fade-up" style="border-radius:var(--r-md);overflow:hidden;margin-top:3rem;box-shadow:var(--sh-md);">
          <iframe
            src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Csokonai+utca+32,+Debrecen+4024,+Hungary&t=&z=17&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed"
            width="100%" height="400" style="border:0;display:block;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            title="BagolykaLand — Debrecen, Csokonai utca 32.">
          </iframe>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

